sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Long story short, Tomoki's house is destroyed. Wandering aimlessly, in search of a place to stay, Tomoki and Ikaros are lent a hand by the class president, Satsukitane. Sohara and Sugata join the mix as they are invited to the home of the town's #1 big shot. They are given a warm reception. But, when they wake up in the morning, there's an angry mob with them!
